COM_methods

Returns the methods name of an COM object.

Syntax

l = COM_methods(h)
l = methods(h)

Input argument

h

a COM object.

Output argument

l

a cell of strings.

Description

methods returns a cell of strings with methods name.

Example

e = actxserver('Excel.Application');
methods(e)
delete(e)
clear e

See also

COM_set.

History

Version Description
1.0.0 initial version

Author

Allan CORNET
